pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-lawmakers-press-top-chip-equipment-makers-details-china-sales-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>宜家首席财务官表示，宜家已准备好应对特朗普领导下的潜在关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ikea-ready-potential-tariffs-under-trump-cfo-says-2024-11-08/</link><description>全球最大家具品牌的所有者宜家周五表示，宜家已经从最近的供应链中断中吸取了教训，并为潜在的贸易壁垒做好了充分准备，因为在唐纳德·特朗普担任总统期间，各公司都在寻求为关税做好准备。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 17:48:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ikea-ready-potential-tariffs-under-trump-cfo-says-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>高夫击败萨巴伦卡，为郑在WTA年终总决赛上上演精彩对决</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/zheng-overcomes-krejcikova-reach-wta-finals-showpiece-2024-11-08/</link><description>周五，美国选手可可·高夫在WTA总决赛半决赛中以7-6(4)、6-3击败世界排名第一的萨巴伦卡，并将在表演赛中迎战中国选手郑钦文。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 17:15:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/zheng-overcomes-krejcikova-reach-wta-finals-showpiece-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>航运需求旺盛，达飞轮船利润大幅增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/cma-cgms-profit-jumps-buoyant-shipping-demand-2024-11-08/</link><description>该航运集团周五表示，强劲的全球需求推高了达飞轮船第三季度的利润，而本季度则出现了从中国发货的热潮，因为该集团淡化了美国可能征收关税的贸易风险。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 16:53:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/cma-cgms-profit-jumps-buoyant-shipping-demand-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，Stellantis与合作伙伴零跑汽车取消了在波兰生产第二款电动汽车的计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-partner-leapmotor-scrap-plan-make-second-ev-model-poland-sources-say-2024-11-08/</link><description>两位知情人士告诉路透社，Stellantis 及其中国合作伙伴零跑汽车已经取消了在这家欧洲汽车制造商位于波兰的工厂生产第二款电动汽车的计划。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 16:34:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-partner-leapmotor-scrap-plan-make-second-ev-model-poland-sources-say-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>巴西企业兜售美国工厂，倾向于特朗普贸易战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brazilian-firms-tout-us-plants-leaning-into-trump-trade-wars-2024-11-08/</link><description>巴西最大的两家工业公司——钢铁制造商 Gerdau 和塑料生产商 Braskem 已经在宣传其在美国的大量业务，以对冲当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的保护主义风险。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 16:15:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brazilian-firms-tout-us-plants-leaning-into-trump-trade-wars-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>马斯克支持的特朗普赢得粉丝乐观，特斯拉市值突破1万亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-hits-1-trillion-market-value-musk-backed-trump-win-fans-optimism-2024-11-08/</link><description>周五，特斯拉市值大幅上涨，收盘突破 1 万亿美元大关，原因是预计首席执行官埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 的公司将在当选总统唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的领导下获得优惠待遇，因为他在民意调查期间获得了广泛支持。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 16:09:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-hits-1-trillion-market-value-musk-backed-trump-win-fans-optimism-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>世贸组织主席竞选连任没有遭到反对，但可能面临特朗普的反对</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/no-fight-top-wto-job-trump-trade-era-2024-11-08/</link><description>两位消息人士称，目前还没有其他候选人站出来挑战世界贸易组织总干事恩戈齐·奥孔乔-伊维拉在这个总部位于日内瓦的贸易机构的连任，尽管唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫可能意味着她的连任仍不确定。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 16:08:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/no-fight-top-wto-job-trump-trade-era-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>倍耐力董事会中化高管可能违反意大利规定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/sinochem-executives-pirelli-board-may-be-breach-italian-rules-2024-11-08/</link><description>一位高级政府官员表示，意大利正在检查中化集团高管在倍耐力董事会的存在是否违反了罗马为保护这家轮胎制造商自主权而实施的措施。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 14:53:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/sinochem-executives-pirelli-board-may-be-breach-italian-rules-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国最新刺激措施未达预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-latest-stimulus-falls-short-expectations-2024-11-08/</link><description>周五，投资者希望中国宣布为唐纳德·特朗普再次当选总统的经济提供额外的财政缓冲，但他们感到失望。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 12:10:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-latest-stimulus-falls-short-expectations-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>分析师对中国提高地方政府债务上限的反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-china-raises-local-government-debt-ceilings-revive-economy-2024-11-08/</link><description>中国最高立法机构周五批准了一项法案，允许地方政府在三年内发行6万亿元人民币（合8,388亿美元）的债券，以置换表外或“隐性”债务，因为政策制定者试图刺激低迷的经济。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 10:20:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/view-china-raises-local-government-debt-ceilings-revive-economy-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国、关税担忧导致欧洲股市连续第三周下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-muted-luxury-firms-fall-2024-11-08/</link><description>欧洲基准斯托克 600 指数周五连续第三周下跌，原因是中国刺激措施效果不佳，以及对特朗普总统任期内关税损害经济增长的担忧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 08:31:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-muted-luxury-firms-fall-2024-11-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>